com.iland.core.api.vcd.event

Interface TypeVappTemplate


  • public interface TypeVappTemplate
    VCD Extension Notification Type for vApp Template.

    See http://pubs.vmware.com/vcd-51/topic/com.vmware.ICbase/PDF/vcd_51_api_guide .pdf

    Author:
    Julien Anguenot

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_CREATE
      A vApp template was created.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_CREATE_REQUEST
      A request to create a vApp template was blocked pending administrative action.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_DELETE
      A vApp template was deleted.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_DELETE_REQUEST
      A request to delete a vApp template was blocked pending administrative action.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_IMPORT
      A virtual machine was imported from vSphere as a vApp template.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_IMPORT_REQUEST
      A request to import a vApp template was blocked pending administrative action.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_MODIFY
      One or more properties of a vApp template were modified.
      static String VAPP_TEMPLATE_MODIFY_REQUEST
      A request to modify a vApp template was blocked pending administrative action.
